author: henning
msg: This is the promised patch to make it possible to set "default values" for
input fields in intake. You can now add a defaultValue attribute to a field
definition and whenever the values are pulled with getDefault() from the
PullHelper, this value is used instead of the empty value. There is a small
documentation patch included, but I think I will prepare a small code
